<p>The Yeoman workflow is comprised of three core tools for improving your productivity and satisfaction when building a web app. These tools are:</p>

<ul>
	<li><a href="https://github.com/yeoman/yo">yo</a>&nbsp;- the scaffolding tool from Yeoman</li>
